e: ￹`Awaay~ `to~ `ko~ `to'eman~. `Sa~`ta'engad~ `sato~ `imatini~.￺It isn't dark anymore. It has turned light.￻黑暗去了，黎明隨即而來
￹`O~ `pa~`ta'engaday~ `to~ `faloco'~ `ita~ `ko~ `sowal~ `no~ `Kawas~.￺The Word of God brings light to our hearts.￻上帝的話帶給我們亮光
￹`Taengad~ `ko~ `pising~ `nira~.￺His face is alight / he is happy.￻他的臉上充滿喜悅
d.f: ￹￺light * diffused without reference to the source￻亮光，光明普照來並未指明其來源
